OL,3,CWoman, 78, named after fatal Jersey
OL,4,Ccar crash
OL,6,FLinda O'Brien, known as Margaret, has
OL,7,Fbeen named by police as the 78-year-
OL,8,Fold woman who died in a road traffic
OL,9,Fcollision in Jersey.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,Fincident between two vehicles on Route
OL,13,Fdes Genets, in St Brelade, at
OL,14,Fapproximately 2:50pm on Sunday 7 June.
OL,16,FMs O'Brien was the only person taken
OL,17,Fto hospital, where she later died.
