OL,3,CWoman, 78, named after fatal Jersey
OL,4,Ccar crash
OL,6,FThe States of Jersey Police confirmed
OL,7,Fthat an investigation into the
OL,8,Fincident "remained ongoing" with "all
OL,9,Flines of enquiry being considered",
OL,10,Fincluding findings from the post-
OL,11,Fmortem.
OL,13,FThe second driver is "assisting police
OL,14,Fwith enquiries as a key witness" and
OL,15,Fno one else is believed to have been
OL,16,Finvolved, according to a police
OL,17,Fspokesperson.
OL,19,FThe force adds: "Our thoughts remain
OL,20,Fwith the family and loved ones of
OL,21,FMargaret during this difficult time."
